<BaseLayout title="About" description="About David Berube." path="/about/" image="/og/about.png"><h1>About.</h1><div class="prose"><p>David Berube works at the edge of product judgment, software delivery, and practical automation. The through-line is making complex systems legible enough to change.</p><p>This site is a public notebook for builds, essays, and agents worth keeping.</p></div><section class="section">{releases.map(([version,years,status,note])=><div class="list-row"><div class="gutter"><strong>{version}</strong><span>{years}</span></div><div><span class="release-status">{status}</span><p class="entry-desc">{note}</p></div></div>)}</section><p class="lede"><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/davidberube/">Full history on LinkedIn →</a></p><p class="serif-lede" style="font-style:italic">The personal line goes here; it should stay quieter than the work.</p><p class="lede" style="color:var(--muted)">Advisory note: this page uses placeholders David will replace with exact company names and dates.</p></BaseLayout>
